9ded			.DUP: 
9ded			CWHEAD .ZDUP OPCODE_DUP "DUP" 3 WORD_FLAG_CODE 
9ded 17				db WORD_SYS_CORE+OPCODE_DUP             
9dee 36 9e			dw .ZDUP            
9df0 04				db 3 + 1 
9df1 .. 00			db "DUP",0              
9df5				endm 
# End of macro CWHEAD
9df5			; | DUP ( u -- u u )     Duplicate whatever item is on TOS | DONE 
9df5			; | | >[!NOTE] 
9df5			; | | > If the duplicated item is a string it is safely duplicated 
